#: ../generic/server/C/web-servers.xml:700(para) ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1952(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/web-servers.xml:700(para)
msgid ""
"You will be prompted to enter the passphrase. Once you enter the correct "
