#: ../generic/server/C/network-config.xml:468(para) ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:939(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/network-config.xml:468(para)
msgid ""
"You also need to edit /etc/default/dhcp3-server to specify the interfaces "
