"para TLS e configurado no <application>postfix</application>."

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2980(para) ../generic/server/C/mail.xml:183(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/mail.xml:183(para)
msgid ""
"Now, the file <filename>/etc/postfix/main.cf</filename> should look like "
"<ulink url=\"../sample/postfix_configuration\">this</ulink>."
